elements.name: Verify that user can successfully delete stock table in UI

steps.name: User is on the Homepage after sign in
the user clicks on the delete button
a pop-up modal should appear with the text: Are you sure you want to delete this record?
the user clicks on Ok button
the modal should close and the system should delete that particular stock from the table view

elements.name: Verify that user can navigate from deleting a stock back to home page

steps.name: User is on the Homepage after sign in
the user clicks on the delete button
a pop-up modal should appear with the text: Are you sure you want to delete this record?
the user clicks on Cancel button
the modal should close without anything been deleted
